textBeforeTable: This is the primary radio system for all public safety first responders in Macomb County. Michigan's Public Safety Communications System (MPSCS)     Project 25 Phase I     Most mobiles and portables on the County Fire Net frequencies transmit with 123.0 PL and receive from their base with another specific PL tone. Do not set your scanner to a specific tone, if you intend on monitoring the entire county net.
